//README

This repository is for a battleship game, currently hotseat only but if 
there is time, two player by web. 

We developed the game using the following languages and frameworks:
	Javascript
	Meteor client/server framework
	Gagarin testing framework    - Jasmin and Velocity testing 


Gagarin Tutorials:
https://hackpad.com/ep/pad/static/RzdMvlwyYHV
https://github.com/anticoders/gagarin

Jasmin Tutorials: 

(actually works with velocity and jasmine so far)
http://www.mhurwi.com/test-driven-meteor-very-basic-tutorial/

another tutorial just for jasmine (testing only javascript)
http://code.tutsplus.com/tutorials/testing-your-javascript-with-jasmine--net-21229

example code of jasmine and meteor together:
https://github.com/meteor-velocity/velocity-examples/blob/master/leaderboard-jasmine/leaderboard.js

